_:Nb1c5b386802c42eb855aa74e5cc29b26 <http://schema.org/description> "The House of Lords Appointments Commission (HOLAC) recommends individuals for appointment as non-party-political life peers and vets nominations for life peers to ensure the highest standards of propriety. HOLAC is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Cabinet Office ." .
